Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.82,0:00:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種速度和操控的確有威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的行動方式有一定的規律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初的攻擊會從正面過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要正面衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的攻擊被迴避掉後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了防止接下來的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會立刻移動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀取移動資料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.76,0:00:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S57
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:40.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種場合的下一個動作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是往後方移動保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐標是X23
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.47,0:00:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看破了我們算計他的行動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱雀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:13.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:14.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給下一步的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止的全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布里塔尼亞有母親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有家臣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有學友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說是第一個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是突然而來的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本軍在將人型自在戰鬥裝甲騎KnightMare Frame
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投入實戰的布里塔尼亞軍面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法抵抗而被擊破了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又要被交給別的人家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是樞木的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次要去本家那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續走  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  這種奇怪的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是在垃圾場的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.18,0:04:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.05,0:04:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會把布里塔尼亞毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:40.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在護靈車的前面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.70,0:04:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那時發誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不原諒奪走我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉的雙眼和雙腿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.10,0:04:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朱雀人生的布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:04:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了創造妹妹娜娜莉能幸福生活的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把世界毀壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有都改變
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要公佈了啊  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我死了這件事就會被公開
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果不想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.04,0:05:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡全力讓我們逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的男人也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個男人交給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞卿  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給他們  誰也不許出手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威爾卿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的11區人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.59,0:05:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傑雷米亞卿  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了  不准出手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡全力放過他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬畏我們  追求我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的名字是  黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.31,0:06:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在有力量的人攻擊沒有力量的人的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會再出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論那敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有多麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有力量之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏懼我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無力之人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追求我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界  由我們黑色騎士團來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要某個人勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭就能結束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我成為了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建立了黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才睡著了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣你也不用敲我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿修佛德學園學生會副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我表面的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為布里塔尼亞學生過著無聊的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一的問題就是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個喜歡慶典的學生會長喜歡給人添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女逆轉慶典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對靜音宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓祭典  還要化裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡還能容忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她說了我還是會奉陪的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有那個『小學生的一天』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉看起來很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都默許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從來到這個學園
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.71,0:07:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉變的總是充滿笑容了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  現在朱雀也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從7年前那個夏天以來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分別至今的朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:04.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓他們知道我就是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.56,0:08:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果變成這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.02,0:08:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣平日的生活就會被毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不保護
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.43,0:08:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻貓怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個假面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個ZERO的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剛才看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 該用時還是要用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是學生會長米蕾·阿修佛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.19,0:08:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立即去抓在校內逃竄的貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,課外活動全部暫停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助我們的社團可以享受經費優待
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來追貓?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.71,0:09:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.52,0:09:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趕快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  學生會長說要抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  你快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓就由我來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是我比較擅長運動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次小鳥逃掉的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把那麼久的事拿出來提
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過七年前而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一如既往的體力笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明更加個人主義的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的事都在我計劃的範圍以內
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那台白色的KnightMare出現以前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚮導兵器Z01 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用SandBoot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用最大戰速沿液狀斜面上升
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援總督
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  想要問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你極端討厭人的死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻願意在軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓人死才會在軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種純真總有一天會害死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lancelot 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總督  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是嗎  又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.69,0:11:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮二式把白殼的傢伙毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的突破力是個障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.62,0:11:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打倒這個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就憑這種武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:13.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍  向撤退路線移動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下去會成為消耗戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去追ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只不過是能源沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特派報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.19,0:12:49.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始俘獲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.67,0:13:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我  朱雀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想自從那時開始那傢伙就改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稱呼自己為『我』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前是自稱『本人』的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.80,0:13:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\rSTAFF}[前者『僕』相對比較謙卑  後者『俺』相對比較自我主義]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在學校還是裝作不認識吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算現在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.38,0:13:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼去做警察  從內部改變不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.48,0:13:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的做法太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己不做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會坐收漁人之利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來改寫事態
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以審判者自居來得到勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話什麼也改變不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由錯誤的過程得到的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七年以前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到的朱雀是更加個人主義的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著自己和日本的驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,率直的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此而令他淚流滿面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這個意義上來講並不是全部都改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  確實有所不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.32,0:14:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要救人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想獲救的是你自己的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以自己想要找死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總是讓自己前往死地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的善意只不過是自我滿足而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:32.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想要得到懲罰的撒嬌男孩而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改變的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.09,0:14:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟有那麼大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法告訴任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直自己背負著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:19.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有那種意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.12,0:15:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.65,0:15:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是被死板的規則所束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是成為布里塔尼亞的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是為了贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我的身邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞已經是一個不值得你去效忠的國家了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要把它改變成有價值的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.82,0:16:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從布里塔尼亞的內部
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為用錯誤的方法得到的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有價值的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.82,0:16:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個小時  軍事法庭就要開庭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個法庭是為了讓你成為犯人而策劃好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.33,0:16:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官也好  法官也好  辯護律師也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便那樣  這也是規則
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會開始打壓11區住民和名譽布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你會死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前  我朋友也總是這麼說我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.73,0:16:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的缺點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也想抓住你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在這兒反而會被反制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是要死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想為了大家而死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨拙的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從以前開始就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.46,0:17:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就是這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才覺得是配得上娜娜莉的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不可能一直陪在娜娜莉的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不是日本人 你為什麼要戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什麼企圖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞的崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.48,0:17:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道能夠實現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.12,0:17:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有不得不完成這事的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:55.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果按現在的計劃一切順利的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要踏上去嗎  修羅之路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果  這是我的命運的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜娜莉能夠敞開心房面對的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以信賴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.62,0:18:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朱雀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.22,0:18:32.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是11 應該是叫樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是克洛維斯殿下那時的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼11在KnightMare裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.85,0:18:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終止影像  這後面的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.37,0:18:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看完
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.97,0:18:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不惜歪曲道理也要活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你失望了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就按照預定把我處刑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.86,0:19:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能在那種地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該在娜娜莉的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是為了這個而來到這裡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然落魄到成為滿足現狀的沒出息的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使否定現在的社會也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人承認而得到能夠改變這一切的力量才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.31,0:19:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你就按那條路走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.70,0:19:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是輸是贏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不使出全力是不會有任何收穫的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對於國家還是個人都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO  要抓住他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.92,0:19:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木准尉Harken Boost解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼是我的最愛食物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別繼續戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的已經達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:10.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用3號道路
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來回答剛才的提問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.19,0:20:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否決定了哪位來當我的騎士的提問
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.17,0:20:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定的成為我的騎士的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在那裡的那位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木朱雀准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀要成為由菲米婭的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓搜查工作能夠確實進行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人助了我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人還說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:57.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17歲的話就應該去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.81,0:21:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時有這個權限的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.76,0:21:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由菲米婭·Li·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以朱雀才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  那時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要救的人是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想的話一切都合理了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.43,0:21:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選擇了由菲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們  而是由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有另一招可用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經把勝利握在手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知道了那個白殼的駕駛員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:43.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是朱雀這個事實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.11,0:23:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝大家長期的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次將把
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二期的OP　解讀不能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及ED　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有OST CD
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.82,0:23:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,節目特製電話卡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後還有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.01,0:23:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從C.C.那兒奪來的CHEESE君Q版魔方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.04,0:23:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起送給10人作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠參與的只有使用MVS的手機登陸手機網頁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯魯修·Vi·布里塔尼亞下令全力的…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我 魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樞木 朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是我的敵人?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠保護娜娜莉的男人成為了由菲米婭的騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是為了保護黑色騎士團的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我來決定嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能不顧全大局嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓世界成為我所希望的樣子
